<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>CryptoMaster – Learn. Trade. Thrive.</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
